{"config":{"lang":["en"],"separator":"[\\s\\-]+","pipeline":["stopWordFilter"]},"docs":[{"location":"","title":"Home","text":"<p>An Act to provide for protection of rights of transgender persons and their welfare and for matters connected therewith and incidental thereto.</p> <p>BE it enacted by Parliament in the Seventieth Year of the Republic of India as follows:\u2014</p>"},{"location":"en/1/","title":"Section 1","text":""},{"location":"en/1/#short-title-extent-and-commencement","title":"Short title, extent and commencement","text":"<ol> <li>This Act may be called the Transgender Persons (Protection of Rights) Act, 2019.</li> <li>It extends to the whole of India.</li> <li>It shall come into force on such date1 as the Central Government may, by notification in the Official Gazette, appoint.</li> </ol>"},{"location":"en/10/","title":"Section 10","text":""},{"location":"en/10/#obligations-of-establishments","title":"Obligations of establishments","text":""},{"location":"en/11/","title":"Section 11","text":""},{"location":"en/11/#grievance-redressal-mechanism","title":"Grievance redressal mechanism","text":""},{"location":"en/12/","title":"Section 12","text":""},{"location":"en/12/#right-of-residence","title":"Right of residence","text":""},{"location":"en/13/","title":"Section 13","text":""},{"location":"en/13/#obligation-of-educational-institutions-to-provide-inclusive-education-to-transgender-persons","title":"Obligation of educational institutions to provide inclusive education to transgender persons","text":""},{"location":"en/14/","title":"Section 14","text":""},{"location":"en/14/#vocational-training-and-self-employment","title":"Vocational training and self-employment","text":""},{"location":"en/15/","title":"Section 15","text":""},{"location":"en/15/#healthcare-facilities","title":"Healthcare facilities","text":""},{"location":"en/16/","title":"Section 16","text":""},{"location":"en/16/#national-council-for-transgender-persons","title":"National Council for 